[2026-03-09 14:39:14] [2ad0bcef-0311-4643-9d88-d57eacf630f4] USER: how can I get javascript to paste on DevTools? 
[2026-03-09 14:39:19] [2ad0bcef-0311-4643-9d88-d57eacf630f4] CLAUDE: When you first try to paste in the DevTools console, browsers block it as a security measure. To enable it:  **Chrome/Edge:** Type `allow pasting` in the console and press Enter, then you can paste normally.  **Firefox:** Go to `about:config`, search for `devtools.selfxss.count`, and set it to a value greater than 0 (e.g., `100`). 
