[2026-03-09 14:40:22] [2ad0bcef-0311-4643-9d88-d57eacf630f4] CLAUDE: The README already explains this. The script is designed to be pasted into the DevTools console:  1. Build it: `pnpm build` 2. Open the file `dist/nico_meets.js` 3. In Google Meet's DevTools Console, type `allow pasting` and press Enter (Chrome blocks pasting by default) 4. Paste the contents of `dist/nico_meets.js` and press Enter  To stop it later, run `__nicoMeets.stop()` in the console. 
